        <w:rPr>
          <w:rFonts w:cs="Arial"/>
          <w:szCs w:val="22"/>
        </w:rPr>
        <w:t>These costs are requested to help to defray publication costs of scientific articles in various peer-reviewed journals as a result of this research.</w:t>
